msgstr "วาด view hierarchy ลงใน image context"

#: src/testing/geisterhand.md:261
msgid "JNI `View.draw()` on Canvas"
msgstr "JNI `View.draw()` บน Canvas"

#: src/testing/geisterhand.md:261
